{"type":"message","id":"9f86287b","parentId":"c4b400e0","timestamp":"2026-03-27T07:10:41.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to correctly spawn a sub-agent with required parameters. The error said:\n\n- mode=\"session\" requires thread=true so the ACP session can stay bound to a thread.\n\n- Also \"task required\" error indicates the \"task\" field is required.\n\nWe need to provide a task description and set thread:true, mode: \"session\"? Let's check signature:\n\n`sessions_spawn` takes fields:\n\n- task: string (required)\n- label: string\n- runtime: string (enum [\"subagent\",\"acp\"])\n- agentId: string (optional)\n- resumeSessionId: string\n- model: string\n- thinking: string\n- cwd: string\n- runTimeoutSeconds: number\n- timeoutSeconds: number\n- thread: boolean\n- mode: string (enum [\"run\",\"session\"])\n- cleanup: string\n- sandbox: string\n- streamTo: string\n- attachments: array\n- attachAs: object\n\nWe need to spawn an isolated sub-agent or ACP coding session.\n\nIn main session, we can spawn a sub-agent with runtime=\"subagent\" or runtime=\"acp\". The earlier error said mode=\"session\" requires thread=true. The mode defaults to \"run\"? In prompt: \"spawn an isolated sub-agent or ACP coding session (runtime=\"acp\" or runtime=\"subagent\"). mode=\"run\" is one-shot and mode=\"session\" is persistent/thread-bound.\"\n\nThus to spawn a sub-agent, we probably use runtime=\"subagent\" and mode=\"run\"? Or maybe we want mode=\"session\"? The user wants a quick agent creation; we likely want a one-shot? Actually they want an agent created, maybe a persistent sub-agent.\n\nWe tried mode=\"session\" but needed thread=true. So we set thread:true and maybe set mode=\"session\"? But then we also need a task description. Let's try:\n\n- task: \"选品专家\" or description.\n\n- label: \"选品专家\"\n\n- runtime: \"subagent\" (or \"acp\"? The runtime determines the type of session. runtime=\"subagent\" spawns a sub-agent; runtime=\"acp\" spawns an ACP coding session. Probably subagent is appropriate.\n\n- mode: \"session\" maybe persistent.\n\n- thread: true (since mode=\"session\" requires thread)\n\n- agentId: maybe \"product-selector\"\n\n- cwd: default?\n\nThus call:\n\n{\n  \"thread\": true,\n  \"task\": \"选品专家，负责快速选品、市场调研、竞品分析，能够评估产品潜力和市场价值\",\n  \"label\": \"选品专家\",\n  \"runtime\": \"subagent\",\n  \"agentId\": \"product-selector\",\n  \"mode\": \"session\"\n}\n\nCheck required fields: task required. The tool will accept.\n\nLet's do that.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9a07f47a7b3e4bcaa4c801d4","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"thread":true,"task":"选品专家，负责快速选品、市场调研、竞品分析，能够评估产品潜力和市场价值","label":"选品专家","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"product-selector","mode":"session"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/free","usage":{"input":45633,"output":1361,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774595434119,"responseId":"gen-1774595435-mnyhJMqkY8d8SV6s73d2"}}
