{"type":"message","id":"0e1cb7d3","parentId":"df2bca97","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:10:26.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" Skills是注入到会话中的能力模块。但用户想要的是注册一个persistent的agent，可以用`openclaw agents register`命令。\n\n让我查看是否有agent注册命令：\n```bash\nopenclaw agents --help\n```\n\n或者查看其他扩展是否包含agent定义。\n\n从之前的子代理创建来看，系统似乎只有主代理是常驻的，子代理是通过sessions_spawn动态创建的。但用户明确要求\"完整注册\"，可能希望创建一个可以随时调用的固定代理。\n\n让我搜索OpenClaw文档中关于\"register agent\"的内容。可能在openclaw-lark插件中定义了子代理的创建Hook，但需要检查插件是否支持。\n\n让我查看openclaw-lark的package.json看看它声明了哪些hooks。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c04de88106ae4c42b4b9fdf8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/package.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/free","usage":{"input":1080,"output":438,"cacheRead":69376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70894,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774609813086,"responseId":"gen-1774609814-m634xJpzN0XsMb5iqfdl"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b669f4c","parentId":"0e1cb7d3","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:10:26.348Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c04de88106ae4c42b4b9fdf8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"@larksuite/openclaw-lark\",\n  \"version\": \"2026.3.25\",\n  \"description\": \"OpenClaw Lark/Feishu channel plugin\",\n  \"bin\": {\n    \"openclaw-lark\": \"bin/openclaw-lark.js\"\n  },\n  \"main\": \"index.js\",\n  \"files\": [\n    \"**/*\"\n  ],\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk\": \"^1.59.0\",\n    \"@sinclair/typebox\": \"0.34.48\",\n    \"image-size\": \"^2.0.2\",\n    \"openclaw\": \"^2026.3.13\",\n    \"zod\": \"^4.3.6\"\n  },\n  \"openclaw\": {\n    \"extensions\": [\n      \"./index.js\"\n    ],\n    \"channel\": {\n      \"id\": \"openclaw-lark\",\n      \"label\": \"Feishu\",\n      \"selectionLabel\": \"Lark/Feishu (飞书)\",\n      \"docsPath\": \"/channels/feishu\",\n      \"docsLabel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"blurb\": \"飞书/Lark enterprise messaging with doc/wiki/drive/task/calendar tools.\",\n      \"aliases\": [\n        \"lark\"\n      ],\n      \"order\": 35,\n      \"quickstartAllowFrom\": true\n    },\n    \"install\": {\n      \"npmSpec\": \"@larksuite/openclaw-lark\",\n      \"localPath\": \"extensions/feishu\",\n      \"defaultChoice\": \"npm\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"types\": \"index.d.ts\",\n  \"exports\": {\n    \".\": {\n      \"types\": \"./index.d.ts\",\n      \"import\": \"./index.js\",\n      \"default\": \"./index.js\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774609826333}}
