{"type":"message","id":"bc205e75","parentId":"c7216120","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:11:02.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"插件没有声明subagent hooks。让我检查openclaw核心包中关于subagent spawning的文档。搜索关键词\"subagent_spawning\"。\n\n实际上，从错误信息来看，系统是支持子代理的，但需要特定条件：\n- `mode=\"session\"` 需要 `thread=true`\n- `thread=true` 需要 \"channel plugin registered subagent_spawning hooks\"\n\n这表明子代理的持久化注册可能需要在插件中实现`subagent_spawning` hook。\n\n对于用户的请求\"完整注册到系统中\"，目前OpenClaw似乎没有独立的agent配置文件，而是通过：\n1. 使用 `sessions_spawn` 动态创建子代理（临时）\n2. 或者等待管理员在插件中注册子代理hook\n\n我可以：\n1. 向用户解释当前的限制\n2. 提供变通方案：创建一个技能（skill）来模拟选品agent的功能\n3. 或者创建一个启动脚本，每次使用时自动spawn选品子代理\n\n但用户明确要求\"创建agent文件、注册到main agent的子agent列表、更新系统agent配置清单\"，这说明用户期望持久化的注册方式。\n\n让我检查是否有其他插件实现了子代理注册。搜索openclaw-lark或其他扩展中是否包含\"subagent\"相关代码。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f0a23547f8864efa9215704f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"subagent_spawning\" /home/halei/.openclaw/extensions/ 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/free","usage":{"input":71064,"output":700,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774609842101,"responseId":"gen-1774609851-peDIJqLtvlTrmqK0aZxd"}}
